ingredients.ingredient: 1 package Duncan Hines® Moist Deluxe® Swiss Chocolate Cake Mix
1 tub Duncan Hines® Creamy Home-Style Classic Vanilla Frosting
15 miniature peanut butter cup candies, halved

cookingTips: Swirl peanut butter into vanilla frosting rather than fully blending for marbled effect
Top cupcakes while frosting is still soft so peanut butter cups adhere better
enrichment.coachingPrompt: Suggest ways to customize boxed mix for a more homemade taste with peanut butter filling.
